This is a python program that automatically sends customized email wishes(Birthday /anniversary / etc) from your desired mail address(without you opening it).
All the user has to do is to maintain an excel file in the given format.
Also before running the python program one must enter their email id and password where it is marked.
The program reads the excel file, verifies the birthdate given in the file with todays date, and if it matches, sends a customized email on the person's given mail address in excel file
